## CUSTOMER LIFETIME VALUE (LTV) CALCULATION

### LTV Components
Average Order Value: ₹_______
Purchase Frequency (per month): _______
Customer Lifespan (months): _______
Gross Margin: _____%

### LTV Calculation Methods

#### Method 1: Simple LTV
LTV = (Average Order Value × Purchase Frequency × Customer Lifespan) × Gross Margin%
LTV = (₹_____ × _____ × _____) × ____% = ₹_______

#### Method 2: LTV with Churn Rate
Monthly Churn Rate: _____%
Customer Lifetime = 1 ÷ Monthly Churn Rate = _____ months
Monthly Revenue per Customer = ₹_______
LTV = (Monthly Revenue ÷ Monthly Churn Rate) × Gross Margin% = ₹_______

#### Method 3: Cohort-Based LTV
Month 1 Revenue: ₹_____ (from 100 customers)
Month 3 Revenue: ₹_____ (customers remaining: _____)
