## CAC MONITORING DASHBOARD

### Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)
Daily Tracking:
- [ ] Ad spend by channel
- [ ] Leads generated by source  
- [ ] Conversion rates at each stage
- [ ] Daily CAC calculation

Weekly Tracking:
- [ ] Weekly CAC by channel
- [ ] Lead quality assessment
- [ ] Sales cycle length analysis
- [ ] Customer onboarding success rate

Monthly Tracking:
- [ ] Monthly CAC trends
- [ ] LTV:CAC ratio analysis
- [ ] Channel performance review
- [ ] Budget reallocation decisions

### Red Flag Indicators
- [ ] CAC increasing >20% month-over-month
- [ ] LTV:CAC ratio falling below 2:1
- [ ] Payback period >12 months
- [ ] Customer churn rate >5% monthly
- [ ] Conversion rates declining consistently

### Action Triggers
If CAC increases by >15%:
- [ ] Immediate channel analysis
- [ ] Landing page audit
- [ ] Competitor analysis
- [ ] Sales process review

If LTV:CAC falls below 2:1:
- [ ] Pricing review
- [ ] Upselling strategy implementation
- [ ] Churn reduction initiatives
- [ ] CAC optimization sprint

